{"tid":996341,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"愛心一百次 - 飛天少女豬事丁","createTime":"2019-01-26T08:10:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-26T11:08:28.000Z","uid":42446,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"62a1fef4088f37864426920ecb879ee9211e1a06","tid":996341,"uid":42446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T08:10:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yzs1ofFqNKQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fyzs1ofFqNKQ&d=ecqA8VcJpUD8b%2BkdJcszuf9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=26652e7a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yzs1ofFqNKQ</a><br />\n<br />\n粉紅粉紅趣緻的臉<br />\n我叫一聲即可飛上天<br />\n赤色絲巾圍在肩<br />\n凝望鏡盒身體會變<br />\n<br />\n隱藏隱藏少女的臉<br />\n我對他不可講出半點<br />\n蘋果圓被 氹氹轉<br />\n太多珍珠怎計算<br />\n<br />\n也許豬的身體不優美<br />\n長鼻短短尾<br />\n但是別人不可天空裡高飛<br />\n<br />\n是我心 無限的純真<br />\n珍珠珍貴像信心<br />\n使我極動人異常吸引<br />\n<br />\n願你知 勇敢的孩子<br />\n應該加點真意和誠意<br />\n愛心不止一百次<br />\n<br />\n一身好本領和才智<br />\n愛心不只一百次"},{"pid":"5ceac12c865400f470f5f485af278c7ed15a828e","tid":996341,"uid":223016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-26T11:08:28.000Z","msg":"喵喵喵都幾有童真 <br />\n<br />\n話說黃汝敏主題開左新post 得閒黎睇下"}]}